#. type: Plain text
#: manual/Configuration.md:821
msgid ""
"You can enable Netatalk's Spotlight compatible search and indexing either "
"globally or on a per volume basis with the **spotlight** option."
msgstr ""
"**spotlight** オプションを使って、グローバルで、あるいは、ボリューム単位ごと"
"に Netatalk の Spotlight 互換検索とインデックス化を有効にできる。"

#. type: Plain text
#: manual/Configuration.md:826
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"> Once Spotlight is enabled for a single volume, all other volumes for\n"
"which spotlight is disabled won't be searchable at all.\n"
